u-boot-sg2002-milkv-duo256m-distroboot (2026.04+~1.8.1-4) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Drop the OpenSBI RTCSYS reset node for Duo 256M. The extra syscon MMIO
    regions exhaust the board's 8 PMP entries and break boot before U-Boot.

