u-boot-sg2002-milkv-duo256m-distroboot (2026.04+~1.8.1-2) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial Debian packaging for the Milk-V Duo 256M distroboot firmware.
  * Build U-Boot from upstream sources and OpenSBI from source.
  * Assemble fip.bin with the local FSBL, DDR parameter block, and RTOS blobs.
  * Set the board's default fdtfile for extlinux fdtdir boot.
  * Install a board-specific u-boot-menu fragment for DTB syncing and overlay
    handling.

 -- Packaging Maintainer <maintainer@example.com>  Sun, 12 Apr 2026 00:06:00 +0900
